#import "/_lib/0.1.1.typ": *
#show: template

#taxon[Definition]
#title[Structure morphism]

The structure morphism of a #local("00BH")[scheme] $X$ is the unique #link("00BF")[morphism of schemes] $pi_X : X -> "Spec" ZZ$.
This is well-defined since $"Spec" ZZ$ is the final object in the category of schemes.
